These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, rabbit, hamster, lizard, bird, chinchilla
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, folk, salsa, metal, hip-hop, r&b, ambient
 1. the fan of ambient is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the fan of classical is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
 3. the fan of classical is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
 6. the owner of the mouse is not the fan of folk##6
 7. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 9. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the fan of folk##7
10. the fan of folk is the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
12. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
13. the fan of classical is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
14. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of classical##7
15. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan of classical##1
16. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8
17. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
18. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of salsa##1
19. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
20. the owner of the hamster is not the fan of r&b##6
21. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
22. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Pet           | bird | rabbit | chinchilla | goat  | lizard  | hamster | mouse    |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | classical   | salsa   | metal | hip-hop | ambient        | r&b |

