.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, juice, soy-milk, water, hot-chocolate, 7up
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific, musical, sports, zombie, romance, spy
 1. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching romance movies is not the person drinking juice##6
 3. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
 4. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person drinking juice##2
 5. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
10. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
13. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
14. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
16. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk | juice    | lemonade | water | milk | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre     | documentary     | romance   | scientific | zombie | sports       | musical        | spy      |

